Chapter 25 : Economic Growth And Sustainability
Chapter 8: Economic growth 
Economic growth is related to GDP 
GDP > - Good economic growth 
GDP < - Negative economic growth
Economic growth of two types : 
Potential Economic growth: 
Is when a countryâ€™s capacity to produce increases. 
Like building more factories 
More machines 

Actual Economic Growth: 
Is the real increase in GDP measured every year
All the resources are utilized efficiently
Example: when the unemployed workers gets job 
A level Note: 
